              <ol marker="(a)">
                <li>
                  <p>
                    <md>
                      <mrow>\revenue=x*199.78e^{(-0.0003x)}</mrow>
                      <mrow>\profit=x*199.78e^{(-0.0003x)}-(-0.0009x^2  + 99.864x + 10050)</mrow>
                    </md>.
                  </p>
                </li>
                <li><p>Recreate the table, but now with the functions we found:</p>
